definitions.definition: A town in the Metropolitan Borough of Rochdale , Greater Manchester , England ( OS grid ref SD8510 ) .
A civil parish near Diss , South Norfolk district, Norfolk , England .
A small village and civil parish north of Westbury , Wiltshire , England ( OS grid ref ST8753 ) .
A town in western Victoria , Australia .
